{"type":"message","id":"b2fa72b9","parentId":"74282acc","timestamp":"2026-04-30T09:14:19.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，我可以直接给你做。\n\n你现在只要发我这 4 样里的任意一种就行：\n\n- 文字描述\n- 草图/照片\n- 关键尺寸\n- 想要的格式（DXF、SVG、OpenSCAD 等）\n\n比如你可以直接这样发：\n\n- 画一个 200mm × 120mm 的矩形板\n- 四角各一个直径 8mm 的孔\n- 孔中心距边 15mm\n- 输出 DXF\n\n你也可以更省事，直接回我一句：\n\n- “先给我一个简单示例”\n\n我就马上给你生成一个 CAD 示例。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00cf43d14e6c06b40169f31d67b66081979cd6fa14034c2e07\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":24608,"output":146,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24754,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777540452650,"responseId":"resp_00cf43d14e6c06b40169f31d6629388197a5c72920f483aa97"}}
