{"type":"message","id":"200c112e","parentId":"4ac70dff","timestamp":"2026-04-30T16:43:44.625Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-05-01 00:42:56 GMT+8] Exec completed (ember-ha, code 0) :: ithub\" to /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/openclaw.json. MCP server \"github\" (/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/openclaw.json): { \"command\": \"npx\",…\nSystem (untrusted): [2026-05-01 00:43:13 GMT+8] Exec completed (nimble-o, code 0) :: MCP server \"github\" (/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/openclaw.json): { \"command\": \"sh\", \"args\": [ \"-lc\", \". \\\"$HOME/.openclaw/secrets/github-mcp.env\\\" && exec npx…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1777567416051-cb7d7837\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-05-01 00:42 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n帮我直接配置进去openclaw mcp里面"}],"timestamp":1777567424352}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e9e99ff","parentId":"200c112e","timestamp":"2026-04-30T16:43:57.906Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"已经直接配进去了。\n\n## 现在状态\n我已经把 GitHub MCP 写进了 OpenClaw 的 `mcp.servers` 里，名字是：\n\n- `github`\n\n## 当前生效配置\n它现在会通过本地 secrets 文件启动 GitHub MCP，而不是把 token 裸写在主配置里。\n\n等价于：\n\n- 从 `~/.openclaw/secrets/github-mcp.env` 读取 `GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN`\n- 启动 `@modelcontextprotocol/server-github`\n\n## 你现在这边已经完成的事\n- OpenClaw MCP 已登记 `github`\n- token 已本地保存\n- 主配置已接入\n\n## 如果你想确认\n你本机可以看到：\n- `openclaw mcp show github`\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以继续帮你：\n\n1. **做一次启动验证**\n2. **顺手把这个泄露过的 token 换掉**\n3. **再帮你接下一个 MCP**，比如 GitHub + OpenPencil 联动\n\n我比较建议下一步先做 **启动验证 + 换 token**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00cf43d14e6c06b40169f386c589fc81979696e557a6d48b0e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":41325,"output":247,"cacheRead":45568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87140,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777567424625,"responseId":"resp_00cf43d14e6c06b40169f386c2815c81978052445e73c6df97"}}
