{"type":"message","id":"3f3a11b8","parentId":"05dcae58","timestamp":"2026-04-30T17:03:08.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好了，已经完成了。\n\n## 已完成\n- 配置了当前仓库 git 身份\n  - 用户名：`openclaw`\n  - 邮箱：`736012150@qq.com`\n- 完成了首个 commit\n- 提交哈希：\n  - `61137bd`\n\n## 当前结果\n你的 workspace 现在已经正式开始用 git 管理这批核心记忆/规则文档了。\n\n首个提交信息是：\n- `Initialize git tracking for memory workflow docs`\n\n---\n\n## 下一步最自然的动作\n现在只差把它推到 GitHub 私有仓库。\n\n你可以接着给我下面任一种信息，我就继续帮你：\n\n### 方式 1，最直接\n把你的 GitHub 仓库地址发我，例如：\n- `https://github.com/你的用户名/仓库名.git`\n\n### 方式 2\n如果仓库还没建，我可以先告诉你：\n- 仓库名怎么取\n- private 仓库怎么建\n- 建完后我帮你接 remote 并 push\n\n---\n\n## 我建议\n下一步直接做一个 **private repo**，名字可以类似：\n\n- `openclaw-memory`\n- `openclaw-workspace`\n- `openclaw-memory-system`\n\n如果你愿意，我下一条可以直接继续帮你：\n**添加 remote + 推送到 GitHub**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00cf43d14e6c06b40169f38b45adb48197acf4c09a9513da06\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":78298,"output":297,"cacheRead":23040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101635,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777568576438,"responseId":"resp_00cf43d14e6c06b40169f38b423a5c8197866103981e89313a"}}
