{"type":"message","id":"5d3e37b7","parentId":"f485aa98","timestamp":"2026-04-30T17:08:33.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我这边没法直接帮你建，原因很简单：\n\n## 当前阻塞\n这台机器上**没有安装 GitHub CLI (`gh`)**，所以我没法直接替你调用 GitHub 创建仓库。\n\n---\n\n## 现在最快的办法\n你自己在 GitHub 网页上建一个 **private 仓库**，只要 1 分钟：\n\n### 建议仓库名\n我推荐用这个：\n- `openclaw-memory`\n\n### 创建选项\n- **Visibility**: `Private`\n- **不要勾选**：\n  - Add a README\n  - Add .gitignore\n  - Choose a license\n\n也就是建一个**空仓库**，避免和你本地第一次 push 冲突。\n\n---\n\n## 创建地址\n你打开这里就行：\n\n<https://github.com/new>\n\n填写：\n- Repository name: `openclaw-memory`\n- Visibility: `Private`\n\n创建完成后，把仓库地址发我，比如：\n\n- `https://github.com/你的用户名/openclaw-memory.git`\n\n我就立刻继续帮你：\n- 添加 remote\n- 推送当前仓库到 GitHub\n\n如果你愿意，我也可以下一条直接告诉你**网页上每一项怎么点**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00cf43d14e6c06b40169f38c8c357c819781816e1bde37b0cb\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1651,"output":270,"cacheRead":100352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102273,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777568904559,"responseId":"resp_00cf43d14e6c06b40169f38c8b00ec8197b6a41cf0b3bf8f1f"}}
