{"type":"message","id":"a598f343","parentId":"b3c5265a","timestamp":"2026-04-30T17:16:52.636Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"SSH 这边也试了，结果是：\n\n## 当前阻塞\n**本机没有可用于 GitHub 的 SSH 公钥授权**，所以 push 失败了。\n\n报错是：\n- `Permission denied (publickey)`\n\n---\n\n## 现在你只差最后一步\n把这台机器的 **SSH 公钥** 加到你的 GitHub 账号里，我就能继续替你 push。\n\n---\n\n## 下一步我建议这样做\n如果你愿意，我下一条可以直接帮你：\n\n1. 检查本机有没有现成 SSH 公钥\n2. 如果没有，就帮你生成一个\n3. 把公钥内容发给你\n4. 你复制到 GitHub:\n   - `Settings`\n   - `SSH and GPG keys`\n   - `New SSH key`\n5. 你加完后，我再继续 push\n\n这样是最顺的。\n\n你只要回我一句：\n\n**“继续检查 SSH key”**\n\n我就直接做。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00cf43d14e6c06b40169f38e80476c81978fd501fe9d9ac03c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1303,"output":214,"cacheRead":101888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103405,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777569405368,"responseId":"resp_00cf43d14e6c06b40169f38e7f12ec819797c4d29d80a5e37a"}}
